WEBVTT

00:01:57.741 --> 00:02:02.223
kuanzisha shule mbadala,
kujenga hospitali, kuchimba visima --

00:02:02.247 --> 00:02:05.184
kwa sababu serikali hazikutaka ama hazikuweza

00:02:05.208 --> 00:02:07.177
kuhudumia wananchi wao.

00:02:07.900 --> 00:02:10.709
Sote tunajua haya masuluhisho ni ya muda mfupi.

00:02:11.455 --> 00:02:14.240
Kuna baadhi ya mambo ambayo misaada haiwezi kutatua,

00:02:15.027 --> 00:02:19.416
kama kujenga mazingira
ambapo wafanyabiashara hujisikia salama

00:02:19.440 --> 00:02:21.251
kuwa watakuwa na fursa sawa

00:02:21.275 --> 00:02:24.517
kuweza kuanza na kuendesha 
biashara zao kwa ufanisi.

00:02:24.541 --> 00:02:26.355
Au kuna mifumo

00:02:26.379 --> 00:02:29.420
ambayo huwawezesha kulinda mali walizovuna.

00:02:29.444 --> 00:02:30.601
Ningependa kusema,